OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrench burkini ban upheld  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas Grenoble loses legal    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fchallenge                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, France's highest administrative court  
OL,6, has upheld a ban on full-body "burkini"
OL,7, swimsuits in public pools, rejecting an
OL,8, appeal by the city of Grenoble.        
OL,10,FLast month, Grenoble authorised all    
OL,11,Fswimwear, including burkinis, sparking 
OL,12,Fa legal battle with the government.    
OL,14,FBurkinis are worn largely by Muslim    
OL,15,Fwomen as a way of preserving modesty   
OL,16,Fand upholding their faith.             
OL,18,FBut the court said it could not allow  
OL,19,F"selective exceptions to the rules to  
OL,20,Fsatisfy religious demands".            
